{"tid":1802543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駐港部隊三軍聯合訓練　模擬登船展開拘捕","createTime":"2019-12-29T14:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T00:20:21.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf7078a600601c6cfb051cddd901e6ee1d50575","tid":1802543,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"解放軍駐港部隊近日進行三軍聯合訓練，駐港部隊下午在官方微博上載演練片段，包括聯合海空巡邏、展開實戰化項目訓練，出動陸軍特戰隊、海軍艦艇部隊，及空軍直升機等。部隊模擬在香港截停可疑船隻，由特戰隊員直升機游繩降落船隻，亦有特戰隊員乘小艇登船，實施拘捕行動。片段未有表示拍攝日期，但投入的兵力較過去多，演習的時間亦較長。<br />\n<br />\n駐港部隊早前在平安夜亦上載片段，顯示在南海某海域展開海上實戰對抗訓練，公開056型導彈護衞艦欽州號，包括指揮所訓練、單艦整體訓練、綜合保障及實際攸用武器等多個內容。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%89%E8%BB%8D%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E7%99%BB%E8%88%B9%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95/?fbclid=IwAR1FD2kpw8mTwGlzhJ3VdAk6dOygd46U1eKc61KSDuRnz6LcrZpUjF4M-6Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A7%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4-%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E6%2593%25AC%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%2588%25B9%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1FD2kpw8mTwGlzhJ3VdAk6dOygd46U1eKc61KSDuRnz6LcrZpUjF4M-6Q&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK97QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=a5524836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A7%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4-%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E6%2593%25AC%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%2588%25B9%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1FD2kpw8mTwGlzhJ3VdAk6dOygd46U1eKc61KSDuRnz6LcrZpUjF4M-6Q&h=3f5d35fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8